commit.message:
Makefile.in (OBJS-common): Reformat, alphabetize, but put insn-*.o first.

	* Makefile.in (OBJS-common): Reformat, alphabetize, but put
	insn-*.o first.
	(OBJS-archive): Reformat, alphabetize.
	(OBJS): Change out_object_file to OBJS-md.

From-SVN: r121081

+	* Makefile.in (OBJS-common): Reformat, alphabetize, but put

+	(OBJS-archive): Reformat, alphabetize.
